data.description: *$5,000 seller assist*   Welcome to this beautiful, well-kept home in the desirable town of Aldan.  This home features a beautiful back yard with a sunroom.  Perfect for entertaining!  Nice size yard with a fire pit area and a pond.  3 bedrooms and a nice size basement that can easily be finished for your needs. The primary and middle bedrooms have lots of built-in storage space.   New flooring on the first floor and a nice open living and dining room.  This home is close to schools, playground and transportation.  Showings will begin on November 14, 2023.
